From 2009 to 2010, the LADA Sport team itself participated in the World Championship, with the Lada Priora WTCC[131][132]. used LADA Sport. For the next two years, the factory team started on the Lada Vesta WTCC[132], and in 2017 privateers from the French RC Motorsport[133] raced on these cars. In the 2010 season, the Formula 1 cars of the Renault team the Lada logo[134] was placed.